com.flowpowered.persistence.config

Class ConfigurationHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.persistence.data.ValueHolderBase
      • com.flowpowered.persistence.config.ConfigurationHolder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationNodeSource, ValueHolder

    public class ConfigurationHolder
extends ValueHolderBase
implements ConfigurationNodeSource
    This object holds a reference to a ConfigurationNode and provides all the methods to get its value, but using the default provided in the constructor
